interpretation: The "baby bottle" card represents nourishment, dependency, and new beginnings. It symbolizes the need for care and support in order to grow and thrive. This card can also indicate a new project or idea that needs nurturing and attention in order to succeed. On the flip side, it can also suggest a sense of immaturity or inability to take care of oneself. The "baby bottle" reminds us to prioritize self-care and seek support when needed.
